snippet.title: Amber Heard Stans Threaten Jennifer Howell
snippet.description:
Today we talk about the tweets Jennifer Howell put out and the vile things that she is being put through by AH stans and her people.  it's utterly disgusting what this woman has been put through for being honest and I want her to know that there's an entire community that is supporting her 

You can donate to my PayPal at: https://paypal.me/TammyTalksAbout 
this is entirely to cover my expenses of attending the VA trial and while not at all necessary,  it is greatly appreciated
